name: From a Town | 01
description: A series of animated portraits accompanied by text, that will reveal a larger narrative over the course of the project. | Goddamn what a waste of a good buzz thought Rodney. He picked at the label of his beer, as Joe started in.  Joe made him uneasy. The guy was like something collapsing in on itself, a terrifying emptiness that would suck you in if you got too close.
